name: Jan Levinson (Melora Hardin from The Office)
description:
If you enjoyed the model I provided, I would greatly appreciate your consideration in making a donation to support my college education.

https://www.patreon.com/user?u=87243198

this was more practice on training person with rtx 3080 with 10vram.

for the dataset I used 10 pictures from the show using vlc.

you can see the dataset here : https://imgur.com/a/GDy1lQH

I used a specific version of dreambooth to get it to work

https://github.com/d8ahazard/sd_dreambooth_extension/tree/c5cb58328c555ac27679422b1da940a9b19de6f2 Here, this is the commit when they first added LoRA.

I added the settings in the pictures of (Jan Levinson 3000 Steps)

modelVersions.name: 6k steps
modelVersions.description:
6k steps but lora unet : 0.0005 , lora text encode 0.00003

so smaller steps , and batch size 1 .
